Description: GUI + CLI internet speed test for Linux
 A native GTK4 + libadwaita speed test with multiple backends:
 Cloudflare (default), Ookla, M-Lab NDT, LibreSpeed, and OVH.
 .
 The interface follows your system light/dark theme automatically
 and ships a non-decorative JSON mode for scripts.
